_text = "The sun is shining down on me as I look out at the scenery in front of me. I remember where I am.\n\nI used to come here to escape. The drive up was enough time to let my thoughts wonder. If I was going through something, I often found myself up here.\n\nIt's ironic really. It's as if my train of thought lead us right back to this place. A place at a literal train bridge. There is an irony in all of this.\n\nThe mind works in mysterious ways. I almost wonder if I had just taken a different path, would my outcome had been different? Would my story have been told differently?\n\nIf only I was a videogame character. I would reload my save over and over figuring out all the different outcomes that I could have experienced.\n\nIf only."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, TheEnd, TheEnd, false)
